(51, '2021-08-27 07:36:11', '2021-08-27 13:06:11', '4', '12', '1344612794.png', NULL, '<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\"> \r\nTemporary Work Permit to Canadian Permanent Residency</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">It is possible for foreign nationals to enter Canada on a temporary work permit before applying for per</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">The following are four Canadian immigration programs available to foreign workers seeking permanent residency:</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">1. Federal Skilled Worker Program (FSWP)</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">If your employer offers you permanent employment while your temporary work permit is valid, you may be able to apply for your permanent residency under the Federal Skilled Worker Program. A job offer of this type is known as arranged employment. Under the Foreign Skilled Worker Program, the temporary worker must reach the required number of points. A number of factors determine the points awarded, such as the applicant\'s age, education, adaptability, language skills, and a job offer. It can take up to 12-18 months to complete this process.</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">2. Canadian Experience Class (CEC)</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">The Canadian Experience Class program allows temporary workers in skilled positions to apply for their work experience in Canada. Temporary workers who are not qualified for the federal skilled worker program should consider this option. The CEC requires applicants to have at least two years of work experience in Canada or to have completed post-secondary studies in Canada and have a year of work experience. To qualify for Canadian permanent residency, applicants must meet one of the requirements above.</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">3. Provincial Nominee Programs (PNP)</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Most provinces have their own Provincial Nominee Program throughout which foreign nationals can apply to become permanent residents of Canada. The applicant should intend to live in the province for which they are applying. While each province provides a variety of choices and options, federal programs often share many characteristics with those in provinces. Under the PNP, permanent residence applications take 12 to 18 months to process. To find out more, please contact us.</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n \r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">4. Quebec Experience Class (QEC))</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Quebec Experience Class is a process for applying for permanent residency for temporary workers. In Quebec Experience Class (QEC), there are additional requirements beyond the Canadian Experience Class (CEQ).</span></span></p><br>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">A candidate under the QEC must have been employed in Quebec for at least one year in a skilled position (through a temporary work permit) and should know an intermediate level of French. By receiving a Quebec Selection Certificate, successful applicants will be eligible to apply for their permanent residence status with the province of Quebec.</span></span></p><br>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">As long as you meet the above-mentioned requirements, foreign nationals in Canada with a Working Holiday Visa can apply through QEC for their permanent residence. Workers on Working Holidays are entitled to this option, especially at the QEC.</span></span></p><br>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Through QEC, a temporary worker can become a permanent resident in as little as one year.</span></span></p><br>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Please contact us today if you would like more information on converting a Work visa into a Permanent Residency visa. Triple I Business offers highly effective solutions for Temporary Work Permit to Canadian Permanent Residency.</span></span></p><br>', 'Get Temporary Work Permit to Canadian Permanent Residency | 100% Guarantee', 'Temporary Work Permit to Canadian Permanent Residency, FSWP, PNP, CEC, QEC', 'Canadian immigration programs for temporary foreign workers to apply for, in order to get their Canadian permanent residency.', 'temporary-work-permit-to-canadian-permanent-residency', NULL, NULL, 'Temporary Work Permit to Canadian Permanent Residency'),
(54, '2021-08-20 12:31:17', '2021-08-20 18:01:17', '4', '13', '1871784876.jpg', 'Global Talent Stream Program (GTS)', '<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\"> \r\nWhat is the Global Talent Stream?\r\n</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">The Global Talent Stream is part of the Temporary Foreign Worker Program (TFWP), which offers temporary work permits to invite immigrants to Canada to meet certain labour needs. In the TFWP, GTS is the branch for highly skilled workers in specialized professions, giving priority to those with experience in engineering and technology fields.</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">In June 2017, the program was launched as a pilot for two years. Together with Employment and Social Development Canada (ESDC) Immigration, Refugees, and Citizenship Canada (IRCC) administers the program. Thousand of skilled foreign workers have arrived in Canada through the GTS since its introduction, with more expected in coming years. </span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">A permanent part of Canadian immigration was announced in the 2019 Federal Budget by the government, giving Canadian businesses accelerated access to talented global candidates. </span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\"> Do you know how the Global Talent Stream works? - Foreign Workers </span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">A foreign worker needs to be aware that they cannot directly apply to the Global Talent Stream. To apply to the GTS, an employer must be a Canadian and the foreign worker(s) must also be listed. That means you must aim to get a GTS work permit from an employer who qualifies for the program if you wish to obtain one.</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">\r\nA Canadian employer can apply through two Global Talent Stream categories</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Categorize A is an employer who is referred to GTS by a nominated GTS partner and is seeking to hire special and dedicated talent?</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Category B pertains to employers looking to fill positions on the Global Talent Occupations List.</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">If you are a worker who hopes to find a job offer that qualifies for the GTS, you should determine whether your job falls within the definition of \"unique and specialized talent\", or whether your profession is on the list of Global Talent Occupations.</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">If you believe you meet the requirements for one of the GTS categories, your next step would be getting a job offer. Other than building a network of contacts, our experts can even assist you in searching for open positions. Canada even operates a Job Bank Database that can be used to locate positions related to the GTS.</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Additionally, you cannot apply directly to the GTS, so once your employer offers you a job, he or she will need to submit an application containing your information. Upon successful completion of an employer\'s application, they will receive a Labour Market Impact Assessment (LMIA). In approximately 10 business days, this LMIA can be used to apply for a Canadian work permit.</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Then, you\'ll be able to start your new job in Canada once you\'re approved for the work permit!</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">In spite of the fact that GTS leads to only a temporary work permit, the program is a great way to obtain permanent residence in Canada. One year of Canadian work experience is required by several Canadian immigration programs. Canadian Experience and Provincial Nominee Program (PNP) streams make up this category in Express Entry. A year of experience will likely put you in a good position to apply for Canadian Permanent Residency.</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Over one million new immigrants are expected to arrive in Canada between 2020 and 2022. Around two thirds of them will come from economic migration. Canada\'s current immigration system prioritizes highly skilled and experienced workers with Canadian experience for permanent residency, so joining GTS is a smart move for establishing one\'s career in Canada.</span></span></p><br>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Get in touch with our experts to learn more about the Global Talent Stream process. A full range of services is offered by Triple I Business for the Global Talent Stream.</span></span></p><br>', 'What is Global Talent Stream Canada? Get A Work Permit in Few Weeks', 'Global Talent Stream Program, work permit, gts visa Canada', 'The Global Talent Stream is designed for firms in Canada looking for highly-skilled foreign nationals, to achieve growth and fill sought-after occupations.', 'global-talent-stream-program', NULL, NULL, 'Global Talent Stream Program'),
(55, '2021-09-20 05:51:54', '2021-09-20 11:21:54', '5', '15', '1210552588.jpg', 'Canada Investor Visa', '<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\"> Canada Investor Visa</span></strong></h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\"> Federal Entrepreneur Program</span></strong></h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">The Canadian immigration Entrepreneur Program is designed for individuals who maintain a business in Canada and plan to operate it effectively. As a part of this immigration program, Canadians and permanent residents can seek new jobs, which will increase the Canadian economy. The Quebec Entrepreneur Program can be accessed by entrepreneurs who plan to live in Quebec. The Entrepreneur Program is not available to entrepreneurs who intend to live in Quebec.</span></span></p><br>\r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">Immigrant Investor Program</span></strong></h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">By making substantial investments in the Canadian economy, investors can contribute to Canada\'s economy. Those who meet the requirements of this Canadian immigration program may apply for their Canadian permanent residency visas jointly with their close family members (as long as they are not found inadmissible for medical or security reasons).</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">Self-Employed Persons Program</span></strong></h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Self-Employed immigrants are eligible for Canada\'s immigration program designed to attract individuals who plan to become self-employed. If you are self-employed and intend to reside in Quebec, you should apply under the Quebec Self-Employed Program.</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">Start-Up Visa Program</span></strong></h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<h2 style=\"background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0in 7.5pt 0in;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,style=\"font-size: 10px;serif; color: black;\">Entrepreneur Start-Up Visa Program – Business Immigration to Canada</span></strong></h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: ‘georgia’,serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Entrepreneur Start-Up Visa is the first program in the world of its kind and is a new program for Canadians seeking immigration. Applicants with successful Start-Up Visas have a chance to network with private sector organizations in Canada that offer guidance and funding, as well as expertise for setting up and operating businesses in Canada. Canadian permanent residency will be granted to those who qualify under this new immigration program. Businesses need not apply for this program if they are based outside of Quebec.</span></span></p><br>\r\n \r\n<p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: ‘georgia’,serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'georgia\'; color: black;\">Entrepreneur Start-Up Visa is the first program in the world of its kind and is a new program for Canadians seeking immigration. Applicants with successful Start-Up Visas have a chance to network with private sector organizations in Canada that offer guidance and funding, as well as expertise for setting up and operating businesses in Canada. Canadian permanent residency will be granted to those who qualify under this new immigration program. Businesses need not apply for this program if they are based outside of Quebec.</span></span></p><br>', 'Federal Entrepreneur Program | Immigrant Investor Program', 'Canada Investor Visa, Federal Entrepreneur Program, Start-Up Visa Program', 'Canadian Immigration programs for entrepreneurs, investors, and self-employed persons. The Requirements. Investors must meet for Canadian Visa', 'federal-program-for-business-and-investor-visa', NULL, NULL, 'Federal Program for Business and Investor Visa');
